                  <summary change="#add-summary"> A poem in Malay in the Jawi script. A detailed
                     description of the devastating fire of <name type="place"
                           key="7000381"
                           ref="http://vocab.getty.edu/page/tgn/7000381">Singapore</name> in <date calendar="Gregorian" when="1831">1831</date>, composed in <date calendar="Gregorian" when="1847">1847</date> by the author who is also known to be the first journalist to document this event.</summary>
